      <title>特朗普媒体怀疑论者被做空股票，面临艰难的战斗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/trump-media-djt-skeptics-who-get-shares-to-short-face-uphill-battle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的媒体初创公司的股票是美国押注成本最高的股票之一。作为衡量成本的一个指标，一项粗略计算显示，该股需要在下周下跌 12%，卖空者才能收支平衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/trump-media-djt-skeptics-who-get-shares-to-short-face-uphill-battle</guid>
